What an extremely informative chat regarding mindfulness and anxiety.
Speaking with professor/scientist and author @drshaunashapiro and Therapist @kimberleyquinlan we speak about the definition of mindfulness, how to approach mindfulness with compassion, how best to practice mindfulness and the scientific evidence behind mindfulness for anxiety

node.text:
10 being fully recovered 1 being right at the start. Where are you on your anxiety recovery journey?
I was once a 1 which felt like a minus 10 trust me. 4 panic attacks a day not being able to social barely being able to get through each day. But now I’m a 10 and If I can do it, you can too. I’m just a regular guy who was motivated from his friend who had been through an anxiety disorder and also recovered he gave me the strength to carry on, the hope that I wasn’t always going to feel like I did. And I got there. I can’t wait to hear your recovery story when you get there ❤️❤️❤️
-
-
-#anxious #anxiety #recovery #yourstory
